                  "href": "http://www.amazon.com/The-Light-Between-Oceans-Novel/dp/1451681755",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "The Light Between Oceans"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". I'm hoping to be able to read a bit this evening once we get home because I was not able to read much this past week."
          }
        ]
      },
