                "type": "em"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Listening"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "  to Daniel's random music - since he is driving, he gets to pick the music. It's typically not my favorite, but that's okay. :)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "em"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Thinking"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "  that I'm kind of nervous about trying out the new Silver Metro Line tomorrow. The Silver Line just opened yesterday, and it will finally allow me to take the metro to work. I will have to take a shuttle to the metro station and switch lines once along the way, so I'm just hoping that it won't end up being too inconvenient to use. I hate driving in this area because of the crazy drivers and the awful traffic, so I really want this to work out!"
          }
        ]
      },
