              {
                "type": "em"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Needing"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "  to be better about pre-writing blog posts. Bloggers, do you have any tips for getting these done? I always plan to pre-write, but then I get distracted from doing it because I know it doesn't need to be posted by today or tomorrow."
          }
